social_posts.post_text: Manifesting $40 million in sales this year! Let’s buy and sell my friends! 📲508-612-0821

A wise mentor once told me in order to reach the highest level of success, to start investing in real estate. 

Today Brendan and I closed on our 7th property, now owning over $2 million dollars worth of real estate. 

Nothing I love more than building our empire and helping others do the same! 

Reach out to me today to start your real estate journey!

The best time to buy real estate was YESTERDAY. The quicker you can get your clock started, the better it is going to be for you!

I have found my passion - helping people buy and sell real estate. I wake up every morning excited for the day, excited for REAL ESTATE!

If you are looking for top-notch service, the best results and to be educated along the way, I am your girl. 

Who wants to hold the sold sign next?!

Reach out to me today to start your journey! 🏠 

@byrnesrealestategroup

We dove into: 
- The power of real estate to build wealth 
- When and how I knew it was time to jump into real estate full time and say good bye to my teaching career
- My biggest regrets when looking back and starting my investing journey 
- Balancing owning multiple companies 
- Ins and outs of the air bnb business 
- How it is to work with your spouse LOL 

AND SO MUCH MORE! Always happy to share where I came from, how I got to where I am today and my plans on where I hope to go. 

Thankful, blessed and excited for what is to come!
